parameters:
[Amelia] Such incredible magical power...
Stronger than any ordinary demon around here.

[Masamune] It seems that the one we had in the
practice room has escaped.

[Masamune] I wonder if it's related to the recent
increase in magical power.

[Amelia] There's no doubt that we had a negative
influence on the demon dog, right?

[Amelia] Anyway, we have no choice but to
restrain it.

[Amelia] The magical power of the demon dog... is
entering my body...

[Amelia] I don't know, but unfamiliar emotions
are overflowing.
[Masamune] Eh... Is this some kind of magic?

[Amelia] Is it magic...? No, it feels
different...

[Amelia] This might sound strange... but I wanted
to hug Masamune-kun.

[Amelia] I don't understand either... It's really
painful and difficult...

[Amelia] But... in the end, I developed feelings
for Masamune-kun...
[Amelia] I love... Masamune-kun, I love you...
[Amelia] Thank you for being with me.
[Masamune] Was it a magic that affects emotions?
[Amelia] I wonder... how it will turn out.

[Amelia] There are still so many things I don't
know about magic.

[Amelia] But, maybe these are truly the feelings
I have...
[Amelia] I have a feeling like that.

[Amelia] Well, shall we go report that we
defeated the magical dog?
